    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-compression power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and an M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive VANOS service and structural reinforcement of the rear subframe to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension remains true to factory specifications with updated bushings, maintaining the precise turn-in and tactile feedback characteristic of the E46 platform. This example is ideal for the purist seeking a driver-centric machine with documented mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 31500.0,
